Maintainer: Paolo Mainardi (paolo@twinbit.it)
Documentation (not available): http://www.twinbit.it

Based on excellent work of Vincenzo Patruno:

* http://www.vincenzopatruno.org/2010/02/19/application-sharing/
* http://segnalazionit.org/2011/02/un-plugin-ufficiale-wordpress-per-la-visualizzazione-dei-dati-istat-sulla-popolazione/

Thanks to Spaghetti Opendata working group:

* http://www.spaghettiopendata.org/


INSTALLATION
------------
1. Copy istat folder to modules directory.
2. At admin/build/modules enable the istat module.
3. Configure the block at admin/build/block.

PRIVACY ISSUES
------------

Actually proxy is hosted on http://www.vincenzopatruno.org website, next version will have a self hosted proxy service, probably Vincenzo will release the proxy code with MIT license.

You can find an alpha version (not usable at the time of writing) of refactored Proxy service to Istat data: https://github.com/twinbit/Widget-Istat